{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/post/nodejs-memoryleak/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"Tob0c39"}}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p><strong>Node 기반의 SSR(Server Side Rendering) 랜더링</strong> 을 서비스에 도입하다 Memory Leak 이슈를 맞이했다.\nJava 환경의 성능테스트를 준비하면 간혹 겪게되는 이슈이긴 한데. Node.js 도입 시작부터 memory leak 이슈가 튀어나와서 사실 당황스럽긴했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"memory-leak-현상-감지하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#memory-leak-%ED%98%84%EC%83%81-%EA%B0%90%EC%A7%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"memory leak 현상 감지하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Memory Leak 현상 감지하기</h2>\n<p>트래픽이 중요한 서비스다 보니 성능검증을 하지 않을 수 없었다.\n보통 서버에 부하를 주게되면 최고 TPS를 찍은 후 유지된다. 요렇게.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 629px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.920245398773%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"normal tps\"\n        title=\"normal tps\"\n        src=\"/static/d0e93cc1063ab6694a106732cef5b008/63a68/normal-tps.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d0e93cc1063ab6694a106732cef5b008/222b7/normal-tps.png 163w,\n/static/d0e93cc1063ab6694a106732cef5b008/ff46a/normal-tps.png 325w,\n/static/d0e93cc1063ab6694a106732cef5b008/63a68/normal-tps.png 629w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n그런데, 실제 부하테스트를 해보니 다음과 같은 TPS 그래프가 나왔다.</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<p><strong>시간이 지날수록 TPS는 떨어지고,</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.39877300613497%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"memoryleak tps\"\n        title=\"memoryleak tps\"\n        src=\"/static/c533fadb29cb3479f6a801a15da98e6c/a6d36/memoryleak-tps.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c533fadb29cb3479f6a801a15da98e6c/222b7/memoryleak-tps.png 163w,\n/static/c533fadb29cb3479f6a801a15da98e6c/ff46a/memoryleak-tps.png 325w,\n/static/c533fadb29cb3479f6a801a15da98e6c/a6d36/memoryleak-tps.png 650w,\n/static/c533fadb29cb3479f6a801a15da98e6c/01267/memoryleak-tps.png 713w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p><strong>node instance가 사용하는 메모리도 점점 차올랐다.</strong></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40.49079754601227%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"memoryleak\"\n        title=\"memoryleak\"\n        src=\"/static/038b770d871c5145b356279123dea94c/a6d36/memoryleak.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/038b770d871c5145b356279123dea94c/222b7/memoryleak.png 163w,\n/static/038b770d871c5145b356279123dea94c/ff46a/memoryleak.png 325w,\n/static/038b770d871c5145b356279123dea94c/a6d36/memoryleak.png 650w,\n/static/038b770d871c5145b356279123dea94c/c8e86/memoryleak.png 758w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"힙-메모리-프로파일하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%9E%99-%EB%A9%94%EB%AA%A8%EB%A6%AC-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%8C%8C%EC%9D%BC%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"힙 메모리 프로파일하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>힙 메모리 프로파일하기</h2>\n<p>전형적인 <code>Memory Leak</code> 패턴이었다. 그래서 Profile을 해봤다.\n<strong>\"Allocation instrumentation on timeline\"</strong> 을 이용하면 실시간으로 메모리가 릴리즈 되지 못하고 누적되는 것을 손쉽게 확인할 수 있다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 28.22085889570552%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"profile timeline\"\n        title=\"profile timeline\"\n        src=\"/static/ec2b2d4129c4aac2bb670ca74ad887df/a6d36/profile-timeline.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ec2b2d4129c4aac2bb670ca74ad887df/222b7/profile-timeline.png 163w,\n/static/ec2b2d4129c4aac2bb670ca74ad887df/ff46a/profile-timeline.png 325w,\n/static/ec2b2d4129c4aac2bb670ca74ad887df/a6d36/profile-timeline.png 650w,\n/static/ec2b2d4129c4aac2bb670ca74ad887df/e548f/profile-timeline.png 975w,\n/static/ec2b2d4129c4aac2bb670ca74ad887df/3c492/profile-timeline.png 1300w,\n/static/ec2b2d4129c4aac2bb670ca74ad887df/07108/profile-timeline.png 1619w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Memory Leak을 찾는 방법에 대해서는 전에 작성한 다음의 발표자료를 참고해라.<br>\n<a href=\"../memory\">Chrome Devtools를 이용한 Web Application Memory 분석법</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Profile의 상세 내역을 보면 클라이언트 요청시마다 생성되는 <code>ServerResponse</code> 객체가 누적되고 있는 것을 확인해 볼 수 있다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 103.06748466257669%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"serverResponse\"\n        title=\"serverResponse\"\n        src=\"/static/494819646d9d7e9a552e4a14859b5835/a6d36/serverResponse.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/494819646d9d7e9a552e4a14859b5835/222b7/serverResponse.png 163w,\n/static/494819646d9d7e9a552e4a14859b5835/ff46a/serverResponse.png 325w,\n/static/494819646d9d7e9a552e4a14859b5835/a6d36/serverResponse.png 650w,\n/static/494819646d9d7e9a552e4a14859b5835/ebf47/serverResponse.png 688w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n찾았다. 요놈 ㅋㅋㅋ</p>\n<h2 id=\"memory-leak-제거하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#memory-leak-%EC%A0%9C%EA%B1%B0%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"memory leak 제거하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Memory Leak 제거하기</h2>\n<p>문제가 된 코드는 단 한줄의 코드였다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// The request handler must be the first middleware on the app</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">app.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">use</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(handlers.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">requestHandler</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">());</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Sentry Express 적용 가이드 <a href=\"https://docs.sentry.io/platforms/node/express/\">https://docs.sentry.io/platforms/node/express/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>express의 에러감지를 위해 적용해 놓은 sentry의 Sentry.Handlers.requestHandler 에서 Memory Leak이 발생</strong>한 것이었다.</p>\n<p>Sentry 코드의 내용을 확인해보면 Node.js의 domain 객체를 사용하는 간단한 코드로 구성되어 있다.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container github-light-theme grvsc-ps-t4tStz\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">export</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">function</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-10 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">requestHandler</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-11 grvsc-t4tStz-6\">options</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">) {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// ...</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">const</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">local</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> domain.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">create</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">();</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  local.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">add</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(req);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  local.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">add</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(res);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  local.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">on</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-8 grvsc-t4tStz-10\">&#39;error&#39;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">, next);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  local.</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-7 grvsc-t4tStz-5\">run</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">(() </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-5 grvsc-t4tStz-9\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">    </span><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-6 grvsc-t4tStz-2\">// ...</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">  });</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-tiszgT-1 grvsc-t4tStz-1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/getsentry/sentry-javascript/blob/master/packages/node/src/handlers.ts#L233-L255\">https://github.com/getsentry/sentry-javascript/blob/master/packages/node/src/handlers.ts#L233-L255</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Node.js의 domain 객체에서 <strong>Memory Leak</strong>을 유발하는 코드가 있어서 위와 같은 문제가 발생한다.\n<a href=\"https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/26098\">Node.js 11.10.0 릴리즈 노트</a>를 확인하시면 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/api/domain.html#domain_domain\">domain</a>의 Memory Leak 이슈가 해결된 커멘트를 확인해 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[<a href=\"https://github.com/nodejs/node/commit/60c5099f4b\">60c5099f4b</a>] - domain: avoid circular memory references (Anna Henningsen) <a href=\"https://github.com/nodejs/node/pull/25993\">#25993</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Node.js 11.10.0에서는 domain 객체의 Memory Leak 문제가 해결되었으나 <br>아직 Node.js 의 LTS 버전은 10.x.x 이기에 사실상 서비스에서는 Sentry.Handlers.requestHandler를 사용할 수 없었다.</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>결과적으로는 Request Header 정보는 서비스 오류, 장애 대응에 크게 문제가 되지 않기에 Express의 Sentry 탐침 코드를 제거하였다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>참고로 Sentry.Handlers.requestHandler를 적용하지 않으면 아래와 같은 Request Header 정보를 Sentry에서 확인 할 수 없다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 650px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 32.515337423312886%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"requestheader\"\n        title=\"requestheader\"\n        src=\"/static/aef57703ec72a422485e0df1d0b43623/a6d36/requestheader.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aef57703ec72a422485e0df1d0b43623/222b7/requestheader.png 163w,\n/static/aef57703ec72a422485e0df1d0b43623/ff46a/requestheader.png 325w,\n/static/aef57703ec72a422485e0df1d0b43623/a6d36/requestheader.png 650w,\n/static/aef57703ec72a422485e0df1d0b43623/e548f/requestheader.png 975w,\n/static/aef57703ec72a422485e0df1d0b43623/5148a/requestheader.png 1228w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"결론\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EB%A1%A0\" aria-label=\"결론 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>결론</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-sentry를-사용한다면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-sentry%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%9C%EB%8B%A4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"1 sentry를 사용한다면 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Sentry를 사용한다면...</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>Node.js 11.10.0 미만</code>에서는 Sentry.Handlers.requestHandler를 사용하지 않는다.</li>\n<li><code>Node.js 11.10.0 이상</code>에서는 Sentry.Handlers.requestHandler를 사용한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-nodejs-11100-미만-버전에서-domain-객체를-사용하지-않는다\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-nodejs-11100-%EB%AF%B8%EB%A7%8C-%EB%B2%84%EC%A0%84%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-domain-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80-%EC%95%8A%EB%8A%94%EB%8B%A4\" aria-label=\"2 nodejs 11100 미만 버전에서 domain 객체를 사용하지 않는다 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. <code>node.js 11.10.0 미만</code> 버전에서 domain 객체를 사용하지 않는다.</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>참고로 Node.js의 domain 객체는 node.js 10.x.x에서 deprecated 되었다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<style class=\"grvsc-styles\">\n  .grvsc-container {\n    overflow: auto;\n    position: relative;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    padding-top: 1rem;\n    padding-top: var(--grvsc-padding-top, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    padding-bottom: 1rem;\n    padding-bottom: var(--grvsc-padding-bottom, var(--grvsc-padding-v, 1rem));\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    border-radius: var(--grvsc-border-radius, 8px);\n    font-feature-settings: normal;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-code {\n    display: table;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line {\n    display: table-row;\n    box-sizing: border-box;\n    width: 100%;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-line > * {\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter-pad {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter {\n    display: table-cell;\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter::before {\n    content: attr(data-content);\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source {\n    display: table-cell;\n    padding-left: 1.5rem;\n    padding-left: var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n    padding-right: 1.5rem;\n    padding-right: var(--grvsc-padding-right, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem));\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-source:empty::after {\n    content: ' ';\n    -webkit-user-select: none;\n    -moz-user-select: none;\n    user-select: none;\n  }\n  \n  .grvsc-gutter + .grvsc-source {\n    padding-left: 0.75rem;\n    padding-left: calc(var(--grvsc-padding-left, var(--grvsc-padding-h, 1.5rem)) / 2);\n  }\n  \n  /* Line transformer styles */\n  \n  .grvsc-has-line-highlighting > .grvsc-code > .grvsc-line::before {\n    content: